+
+        // [GIVEN] Inventory posted with multiple lots and different expiration dates across multiple bins
+        // Bin 1: LOT01 (30.11.2025): 434.97616 PCS, LOT03 (25.09.2025): 17.3126 PCS, LOT06 (25.09.2025): 17.0373 PCS
